Mortgage the house, I mean.

42:50.100 --> 42:51.294
He didn't.

42:51.340 --> 42:53.774
But he must have.
How else would he get the cash?

42:53.820 --> 42:55.538
Well, that's a funny one, that.

42:55.580 --> 42:59.619
