but you were willing to let that go.

43:10.100 --> 43:12.250
So where's the rest?

43:12.940 --> 43:15.329
It's safe. From you.

43:18.420 --> 43:20.411
Looks like the drinks are on you, then.

43:30.940 --> 43:34.057
Lyle, you had any luck with that flight path?

43:34.100 --> 43:36.660
Oh, that? Yeah, yeah. Got 'em to divert.

43:36.700 --> 43:38.930
Once I had words, they soon listened.

43:38.980 --> 43:41.494
Nobody messes with Lyle Anderson.

43:41.540 --> 43:43.417
(Glasses rattle)

43:43.460 --> 43:46.054
