44:43.580 --> 44:45.411
Ooh, good luck.

44:52.540 --> 44:55.100
Hi. There you go.

44:55.140 --> 45:00.260
I did try and tell you about the bag.
It's clean money, I swear.

45:00.300 --> 45:02.734
